<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1422101-another-book-about-trump-i-already-know">Another book about tRump! I already know about tRump and don&#39;t need to read another book. If he&#39;s still around when I find the book in a library or on the dollar shelf at a used bookstore, I may read it. All most of us can do is not vote for him or any person who would support him. Am I missing something? Is it urgent?</a>
</div>
