<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/55751098-deb-m">Deb M.</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is quite evident you have never read a Bob Woodward book. Woodward is the master when it comes to writing about the goings on in the White House. H<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is quite evident you have never read a Bob Woodward book. Woodward is the master when it comes to writing about the goings on in the White House. He began as an investigative journalist and has written 18 books about American politics. You might want to check out Woodward's credentials before writing this book off.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
